headline: Temple University and Follett Higher Education to Celebrate Grand Opening of State-of-the-Art Campus Bookstore at Paley Hall
summary: Temple University and Follett Higher Education, the largest campus retailer in North America, will soon celebrate the grand opening of an improved campus bookstore housed within the newly opened, LEED-certified Paley Hall. The revamped and relocated campus bookstore is designed to bring best-in-class services, products, and academic support to Temple students and faculty.
